quran[227]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,"Twa, Siiyn, Miiym, (Insiguro y’izi ndome hamwe nuwufise ubumenyi bwazo n’Imana yonyene gusa)"
  26,2,Aya n’amajambo ari mugitabu kimenyesha ibikenewe bijanye n’idini
  26,3,Nkumbure wota umutima wawe murudubi kubera abantu bawe batabaye aba Isilamu
  26,4,Iyo dushaka twari kubamanurira ibitangaro bivuye mw’ijuru hanyuma amazosi yabo akagamburuka nugukurikira bashaka canke badashaka mugabo ntidushaka kutegeka umuntu ngo abe umu Isilamu
  26,5,"Mugabo\tntibashikirwa\tn’icibutso\tgishasha\tkivuye\tkuri\tnyene\timigisha myinshi, mugabo yama ija kure yivyo"
  26,6,"Rero mu vy’ukuri barahakanye kuri ivyo rero ubu vuba, bazoshikirwa n’inkuru z’ivyo bahora bajajurirako"
  26,7,Mbega ntibabonye ngaha kw’Isi ingene twanagishije ibiterwa biri kuriyo n’ubwoko butandukanye bwiza
  26,8,Ntankeka muri ivyo harimwo ibimenyetso mugabo benshi muribo ntavyo bemera
  26,9,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,10,"N’Umuremyi\twawe\tmugihe\tyahamagara\tintumwa\tyiwe\tMussa\t(iiii) amubwira ati:- nugende kuri barya bantu bahemukiye imitima yabo"
  26,11,"Abantu bo kwa Fir’auni ubabwire uti:- mbega ntibatinya Imana"
  26,12,"Nawe avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje mu vy’ukuri jewe ndatinya yuko abo bantu bompakana"
  26,13,"N’igikiriza canje ntiki nyorohereza hamwe n’ururimi wanje ntirutomora amajambo neza, rero nushikirize ubu butumwa kwa mwene wanje Haruna (iii)"
  26,14,Nabo n’abantu bafise amakosa imbere yanje mugabo ntinya yuko bongandagura
  26,15,"Avuga ati:- Oya sivyo, ahubwo ni mugende n’ibi bitangaro vyanje, mu vy’ukuri twebwe turi kumwe namwe kandi turabumva"
  26,16,"Rero nimugende kwa Fir’auni mumubwire muti:- ntankeka twebwe turi intumwa z’Umuremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,17,Turungitswe yuko wobatwarira turi kumwe twese hamwe na bene Israeri
  26,18,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- mbega wewe ntitwakurereye iwacu muugihe wari ukiri mutoyi hanyuma turabana twese kumyaka myinshi y’ubuzima bwawe bwose"
  26,19,Kandi waragize ico gikorwa cawe muvyo wagize vyose uca uba mu bantu badashima
  26,20,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ivuga iti:- naragize ivyo vyose ngaho mugihe nari mu bantu bazimiye"
  26,21,Rero nanje naciye ndabahunga mugihe natinya Umuremyi wanje ubu yarampaye amategeko kandi yarampezagiye ngombe ndi muntumwa z’Imana
  26,22,Kandi uwo niwo mugisha wangiriyeko impuhwe wukubashira mubuja wa bene Israeri
  26,23,"Fir’auni yavuze ati:- ni nde uyo Muremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,24,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa ivuga iti :- n’Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi hamwe nibirimwo nimwaba mwebwe muri mu bantu mwemera"
  26,25,"Fir’aauni\tyabwiye\tabantu\tbamukikuje\tati :-\tmbega\tmwebwe ntimwumva"
  26,26,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) aca avuga ati:- Umuremyi niwe muremyi w’abavyeyi banyu baho hambere"
  26,27,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- ntankeka iyo ntumwa yanyu yarungitswe kuri mwebwe n’umusazi"
  26,28,"Intumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tivuga\titi:-\tUmuremyi\tw’ubuseruko n’uburengera zuba hamwe n’ibiri hagati yavyo nimwaba mutegera neza"
  26,29,"Fir’auni aca avuga ati:- niwakurikira iyindi Mana atari jewe mu vy’ukuri nzokugira nk’abantu bari mwibohero"
  26,30,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ivuga iti:- mbega naho nokuzanira ikintu kiri k’umugaragaro"
  26,31,"Fir’auni nawe amwishura ati:- nukizane niwaba uri mu bantu bavugisha ukuri kwama"
  26,32,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ijugunya inkoni yiwe, mukanya isase ica ihinduka inzoka nyakuri iri k’umugaragaro"
  26,33,Ica isokorora ukuboko kwayo mumpuzu mumwanya isase guca kurera derere kubantu bakubonye
  26,34,"Fir’auni\tavuga\tabwira\tabakuru\tbamukikuje\tati :-\tmu\tvy’ukuri\tuyu n’umurozi afise ubumenyi buhanitse"
  26,35,"Agomba\tabakure\tmugihugu\tcanyu\takoresheje\tuburozi\tbwiwe,\tnone mwebwe mubivuga ko iki"
  26,36,"Nabo\tbavuga\tbati:-\tnimumuhe\tumwanya\thamwe\tna\tmwene\twabo hanyuma mubarungike mugisagara caho bakoraniriza abantu bose"
  26,37,Bazokuzanira ibihangange vy’abarozi bose bafise ubumenyi buhanitse
  26,38,"Barakoranijwe\tabarozi\tbose,\tmumwanya\tn’umusi\twagenewe\turwo rubanza"
  26,39,"Baca babwirwa abantu bati :- none mwese mwamaze gukorana"
  26,40,Nkumbure tuzobakurikira abo barozi niba aribo bazoronka intsinzi
  26,41,"Rero mugihe bashika abo barozi baciye babwira Fir’auni bati:- mbega turaronka impembo nitwa tahukana intsinzi"
  26,42,"Fir’auni abishura ati:- egome kandi mwebwe muzoba muri bamwe mu bantu banje bizigirwa"
  26,43,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ibabwira babarozi iti:- nimujugunye ivyo mushobora kujugunya"
  26,44,"Bajugunya imigozi yabo hamwe n’inkoni zabo nukuvuga bati:- kububasha bwa Fir’auni ni twebwe bene intsinzi"
  26,45,Hanyuma intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ijugunya inkoni yayo hasi yankoni ica iramiragura ivyo abo barozi badukanye
  26,46,Aho niho babarozi bose barwa hasi barapfukama
  26,47,"Baca bavuga bati:- turemeye Umuremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,48,Umuremyi wa Mussa (iii) hamwe na Haruna (iii)
  26,49,"Fir’auni avuga ati:- mbega mwamwemeye uyo Mussa (iii) imbere yuko ndabaha uruhusha? Ntankeka niwe yabaye umukuru wanyu yabigishije uburozi, ubu rero muzotahura neza, ubu ngiye gucagagura amaboko n’amaguru yanyu ndabitandukanije hanyuma nce ndababamba kubiti mwese"
  26,50,"Nabo baca bavuga bati:- ntaco bitwaye mu vy’ukuri twese tuzo subira ku Muremyi wacu"
  26,51,"Ntankeka twebwe twizeye yuko Umuremyi wacu azotugirira ikigongwe kubera ibicumuro vyacu, kuko twebwe tubaye abambere mukwemera kuba aba Isilamu b’ukuri"
  26,52,"Twara\tmurungikiye\tintumwa\ty’Imana\tMussa\t(iii)\tubutumire\tyuko yogenda ku bantu banje mugihe c’ijoro ntankeka muzo kurikiranwa"
  26,53,"Rero\tFir’auni\tyaciye\tarungika\tubutumwa\tbw’ugukoranya\tabantu\tbo mugisagara bose"
  26,54,Mu vy’ukuri abo Bayahudi n’akarwi k’abantu bakeyi cane
  26,55,Nabo n’abantu badu shavuza cane
  26,56,Natwe turi benshi mugabo turabatinya
  26,57,Duca tubakura mu mirima yabo hamwe no mumusoko y’amazi
  26,58,Nukuba kura mububiko bwabo n’ahantu habo heza cane
  26,59,Nuko rero twahaye ibisigi kuri bene Israeri
  26,60,Baca bakurikira k’ubuseruko bw’izuba
  26,61,"Mugihe zabonana ingabo zose uko ari zibiri, abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) baciye bavuga bati:- twebwe duhava dufatwa"
  26,62,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ica ivuga iti:- oya! mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wanje ari kumwe nanje ntankeka azondongora"
  26,63,"Mumwanya twara murungikiye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ubutumwa tumubwira duti:- kubita iyo nkoni yawe kuri ico kiyaga, naco gica cigaburwamwo ibiyaga bibiri no kumpande zose haca haba nk’imisozi mininiya"
  26,64,Duca tuzana ngaho abandi bantu
  26,65,Duca turokora intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) hamwe nabo bari kumwe bose
  26,66,Hanyuma twibiza mumazi abo bandi bantu
  26,67,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tmuri\tibi\tvyose\tharimwo\ticirwa\tmugabo\tbenshi\tmuribo simubemera"
  26,68,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,69,Kandi ubasomere inkuru y’intumwa y’Imana Ibrahimu (iii)
  26,70,"Mugihe yabwira Se wiwe hamwe n’abantu biwe ati:- mbega\tmwebwe musenga ibiki"
  26,71,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- twebwe dusenga amasanamu yamisi yose"
  26,72,"Nawe avuga ati:- mbega ayo masanamu musenga arabumva mugihe muyahamagaye"
  26,73,Canke harico abamarira canke abagirira inabi
  26,74,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- ahubwo twasanze badata bacu bagira uku nyene tugira"
  26,75,"Nawe abishura ati:- mbega mwarababonye abo musenga"
  26,76,Mwebwe hamwe n’abavyeyi banyu babayeho imbere yanyu
  26,77,Ntankeka abo n’abansi banje dukuyemwo Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  26,78,Kuko ariyo yandemye kandi niyo yandongoye
  26,79,Kandi niyo intamika nukunywesha
  26,80,No mugihe nsinzikajwe n’ingwara niyo indonsa akoyokwe
  26,81,Kandi niyo izonyica hanyuma ize insubize ubuzima
  26,82,Kandi niyo nizeye yuko izongirira ikigongwe kubicumuro vyanje k’umusi w’impembo
  26,83,"Muremyi wanje numpe itegeko, kandi umpuze n’abagira ibikorwa vyiza"
  26,84,Kandi umpezagire mukuvugwa kuneza n’abantu bazoza munyuma yanje
  26,85,Kandi umpezagire mubazosigirwa ibisigi vy’imirima irimwo imihezagiro myiza yo mw’ijuru
  26,86,Kandi ugirire ikigongwe Data wanje ntankeka yari mubantu bazimiye
  26,87,Kandi ntuntetereze k’umusi wukuzurwa kw’abantu bose
  26,88,Umusi waho amatungo yabo ataco azobamarira canke ibibondo vyabo
  26,89,Dukuyemwo uwuzoba yatumbereye Imana yiwe afise umutima mwiza
  26,90,N’ijuru rizokwegerezwa ribe hafi ku bantu beranda
  26,91,N’umuriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu uzokwerekanwa icese kubagizi b’inabi
  26,92,"Bazobwirwa bati:- bari hehe abo mwahora musenga"
  26,93,Atari Imana mbega boshobora kubafasha canke kwifashisha bonyene
  26,94,Rero bazotabwa mumuriro udahera hamwe n’abacumuzi bagenzi babo
  26,95,Hamwe n’ingabo za Shetani zose
  26,96,Bazovuga bamwe bahora babasenga mugihe bazoba bariko baratongana bari mumuriro udahera
  26,97,"Ndarahiye kw’izina ry’Imana, mu vy’ukuri twebwe twari mubuzimire buri k’umugaragaro"
  26,98,Mugihe twabagirira ineza n’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  26,99,Kandi ntibatuzimije atari babantu babi
  26,100,Natwe ntidufise abadusabira
  26,101,Canke abagenzi bwite dufise
  26,102,Iyo tuba dufise aho tugarukira twari kuba aba Isilamu
  26,103,"Ntankeka\tmuri\tibi\tvyose\tharimwo\titegero\trininiya\tmugabo\tbenshi muribo s’abemera"
  26,104,Mu vy’ukuri umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,105,Abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Nuhu (iii) barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,106,"Ubibutse mugihe yababwira uwo mugenzi wabo ariwe Nuhu (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimuzotinya"
  26,107,Mu vyukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,108,Rero nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,109,"Kandi\tsindabashakira\tko\timpembo,\tmugabo\timpembo\tyanje\tiri k’umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,110,Rero nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,111,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- mbega tukwemere wewe mugihe abagowe aribo bagukurikira"
  26,112,"Nawe avuga ati:- nomenya gute ibikorwa vyanyu mwahora mugira"
  26,113,Iharurwa ryabo ntarihari atari ku muremyi wanje gusa iyo mwobimenya
  26,114,Nanje sinzo kwirukana abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,115,"Jewe ntaco ndimwo, atari uko ndimubatuza bari k’umugaragaro"
  26,116,"Nabo bavuga bati:- nutareka ewe Nuhu (iii) iryo tuza ryawe ntankeka uzoba uri mubazoterwa amabuye"
  26,117,"Nawe avuga ati:- Muremyi wanje, ntankeka abantu banje banyihakanye"
  26,118,"Rero nuducire urubanza ruri hagati yanje hamwe nabo, urwo rubanza rube rwiza, kandi undokore hamwe nabo ndikumwe nabo hamwe n’abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,119,Kubera ivyo twaciye tumurokora hamwe nabo bari kumwe bose bari mubwato bwari butwaye ibintu vyinshi
  26,120,Hanyuma twibiza mumazi mubasigaye
  26,121,Ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,122,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"
  26,123,Na bene Aadi nabo barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,124,"Mugihe\tmwene\twabo\tHudu\t(iii)\tyababwira\tati:-\tmbega\tmwebwe ntimuzotinya Imana yanyu"
  26,125,Ntankeka jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,126,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, kandi mungamburukire"
  26,127,"Kandi\tntaco\tnshaka\tkuri\tibi\tvyose,\tmugabo\timpembo\tyanje\tiri\tku muremyi w’abantu bose"
  26,128,"Mbega mwiyubakira amazu ahari agatumba, uku n’ugufyinata muriko muragira"
  26,129,Mukiyubakira n’inzitiro nk’uko mubona yuko muzoramba mubuzima bwanyu bwose
  26,130,No mugihe muteye abandi mubatera n’ubwishime
  26,131,Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri kandi mungamburukire
  26,132,Nimutinye uwabahaye ibi vyose muzi
  26,133,Ko ariwe yabahaye ibikoko hamwe n’ibibondo vy’abahungu
  26,134,Hamwe n’imirima n’amasoko y’amazi n’inzuzi
  26,135,Mu vy’ukuri ndabafitiye ubwoba bw’ibihano vy’umusi w’imperuka
  26,136,"Nabo bamwishuye bati:- n’ibisanzwe kuri twebwe\tkuko udushikirije ubwo butumwa canke ntube mubabu dushikiriza"
  26,137,Ntivyari kuba ibi vyose atari uko ari ingeso z’abantu baho hambere
  26,138,Natwe ntituzohanwa
  26,139,"Rero baramuhakana natwe duca tubibiza mumazi, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mu bantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,140,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha hamwe n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,141,Bene Thamuda nabo nyene barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,142,"Mugihe mwene wabo yabwira intumwa y’Imana Swaleh (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,143,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,144,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nanje mungamburukire"
  26,145,"Kandi nanje sindabasaba impembo kuri ivyo, mugabo impembo yanje iri ku muremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,146,Mbega muzosigwa mumahoro muri ibi bintu biri ngaha iwanyu
  26,147,Mumirima hamwe no mumasoko y’amazi
  26,148,N’ibiterwa vy’imitende bifise ivyamwa vyiza
  26,149,Mukabaza n’imisozi nukuyigira mwo amazu yanyu y’ukwinezereza mwo gusa
  26,150,"Nimutinye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nanje mungamburukire"
  26,151,Kandi ntimu gamburukire amategeko yabo bahakanyi b’Imana
  26,152,Nabagira ubwononyi gusa kuri iy’Isi mugabo ntibayigire neza
  26,153,"Nabo bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubantu barozwe"
  26,154,"Wewe\tntanakimwe\turimwo\tahubwo\turi\tumuntu\tnkatwe,\trero nutuzanire ibitangaro niwaba uvugisha ukuri kwama"
  26,155,"Nawe abishura ati:- iyi nyana y’Ingamiya nibe ifise izamu\tryukunywa amazi, namwe mube mufise izamu ryanyu ryukuvoma k’umusi wageneweko"
  26,156,"Kandi ntimuyikoreko ngo muyigirire inabi\thanyuma ntimuze mufatwe n’ibihano vy’umusi w’imperuka"
  26,157,Mugabo abo bantu barayikereye iyo Ngamiya nukuba mumaganya
  26,158,"Rero ibihano birabafata, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo, mugabo benshi muribo ntibavyemera"
  26,159,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"
  26,160,Abantu b’intumwa y’Imana Lutwi (iii) nabone barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,161,"Mugihe yababwira mwene wabo na Lutwi (iii) ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,162,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,163,"Rero ni mutinye Imana yanyu, nanje mu ngamburukire"
  26,164,"Kandi jewe sindabasaba impembo kuri ibi vyose, mugabo impembo yanje iri kumana w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,165,Mbega mwebwe murangura amabanga yabubatse n’abagabo nkamwe mubiremwa vy’imana
  26,166,"Mukareka\tabo\tUmuremyi\twanyu\tyabaremeye\tmubagore\tbanyu,\tmu vy’ukuri mwebwe muri mubantu mwarenze uburimbi"
  26,167,"Nabo bamwishura bati:- nutareka kutubuza wewe Lutwi (iii) ntankeka wewe uzoba uri mubantu bazokwirukanwa ngaha muri iki gisagara turimwo"
  26,168,"Nawe abishura ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndimu bantu banka cane ivyo bikorwa vyanyu bigaritse vy’umwanda"
  26,169,Muremyi wanje nundokore n’aba bantu banje kuri ibi bintu bariko baragira
  26,170,Natwe duca turamurokora n’abantu biwe bose
  26,171,Dukuyemwo umutamakazi yari mubicara inyuma y’abandi bose
  26,172,Hanyuma duca turabahonya b’abandi
  26,173,"Duca tubamanurira imvura y’isegenya mbi cane, nayo yari iyaba gabishijwe"
  26,174,"Ntankeka ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo, mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri"
  26,175,Mu vy’ukuri Umuremyi wawe niwe nyene ububasha n’impuhwe zihagije
  26,176,N’abantu bo mukibira nabone barahakanye intumwa z’Imana
  26,177,"Mugihe intumwa y’Imana Shuebu (iii) yababwira ati:- mbega mwebwe ntimutinya Imana yanyu"
  26,178,Mu vy’ukuri jewe kuri mwebwe nd’intumwa y’Imana yizigiwe
  26,179,Nimutinye Imana yanyu kandi mu ngamburukire
  26,180,"Kandi sindabasaba impembo iyariyo yose, mugabo impembo yanje iri kumuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  26,181,Nimwuzuze igipimo neza mugabo ntimube mubantu bagabanya kuri ivyo bipimo
  26,182,Kandi mupime kuminzani y’ukuri
  26,183,"Kandi ntimuba gabanirize abantu kubintu vyabo, kandi ntimugendere kuri iy’Isi namwe muri mu bantu b’abononyi"
  26,184,Nimutinye uwabaremye hamwe n’ibiremwa vyabayeho vyose
  26,185,"Nabo bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri wewe uri mubantu barozwe"
  26,186,"Na wewe ntiwari bwabeho, mugabo uri mubantu nkatwe, mu vy’ukuri twebwe tukubona nkuko uri mu bantu b’ababeshi"
  26,187,"Rero\tnutumanurire\tibimanyu\tvy’amajuru\tniwaba\turi\tmubantu bavugisha ukuri"
  26,188,"Nawe abishura ati:- Umuremyi wanje niwe afise ubumenyi buhagije bw’ivyo muriko muragira"
  26,189,"Baramwihakanye baca bahura n’ibihano vy’umusi w’igitutu, ntankeka ivo vyari ibihano vy’umusi uhambaye"
  26,190,Mu vy’ukuri muri ibi vyose harimwo ibitekerezo mugabo benshi muribo ntibari mubantu bemera Imana yabo y’ukuri
  26,191,"Mu\tvy’ukuri\tUmuremyi\twawe\tniwe\tnyene\tububasha\tn’impuhwe zihagije"
  26,192,Ntankeka iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu nimanurwa ry’Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose
  26,193,Yamanuye ibi vyose nukunagura intahe y’ukuri kandi yizigigwa
  26,194,Hejuru y’umutima wawe kugira ngo ube mu bantu batuza
  26,195,Mururimi rw’icarabu rutomoye neza ruri k’umugaragaro
  26,196,N’ibi vyose biri mubitabu vy’aho hambere
  26,197,Mbega nticari ikimenyetso kuribo yuko ibi vyose muncabwenge zabene Israeri babizi
  26,198,Nk’iyo tumanurira kuri umwe muribo atari mubwoko bw’Abarabu
  26,199,"Agaca\tabasomera\tayo\tmajambo\tntibari\tkuba\tmubemera\tbimwe vy’ukuri"
  26,200,Uku rero niko twinjiza mumishaha y’abantu babi
  26,201,Nabo ntibazo kwemera kugeza aho bazobona ibihano bibabaza
  26,202,Rero bazoshikirwa n’ivyo bihano giturumbuka nabo batabizi
  26,203,"Bazovuga bati:- mbega twebwe tuzoronswa akanya"
  26,204,Mbega bahimiriza kubihano vyacu
  26,205,Ubibona gute nk’iyo twobanezereza nk’imyaka myinshi
  26,206,Hanyuma ivyo bihano bibashikire nkuko bavyemerewe
  26,207,Bizobamarira iki muvyo banezerejwe
  26,208,"Kandi ntitwahoneje igisagara icarico cose, n’uko hari abatuza abantu"
  26,209,N’icibutso mugabo ntitwari mubahemukiye imitima yacu
  26,210,Nayo mashetani ntiyamanutse n’iyi Qur’aani ntagatifu
  26,211,Kandi ntibiba kuribo kandi ntibabishoboye
  26,212,Ntankeka barazitiwe mukwumva
  26,213,Rero ntuze usabe iyindi Mana hamwe n’Imana y’ukuri kugira ngo ntuze ube mu bantu bazohanwa n’Imana
  26,214,Utuze abantu bawe muri kumwe nabo n’abari hafi yawe
  26,215,"Kandi\twunamike\tibaba\tryawe\tkuri\turya\tagukurikira\tmuri\tbarya bakwemeye"
  26,216,"Nibiyonkora wewe nuvuge uti:- jewe ndikure yivyo muriko muragira"
  26,217,Kandi wizere Umuremyi wawe gusa afise ububasha n’Impuhwe zihagije
  26,218,Kuko ariwe akubona aho uhagaze hose
  26,219,N’ihindagurika ryawe ryose hamwe n’abapfukama bose bashize imitwe yabo hasi
  26,220,Mu vy’kuri Imana niyo yumva kandi niyo nyene ubumenyi buhagije
  26,221,Mbega ndababwire mubo Amashetani yama amanukirako
  26,222,Amanukira k’umuntu mukuru wumwadukizi w’ikintu afise ibicumuro bininiya cane
  26,223,"Babashikiriza amajambo bumvise, mugabo benshi muribo n’ababeshi gusa"
  26,224,N’abategura amajambo y’ubuhizi bakurikiranwa n’abantu bazimiye
  26,225,Mbega ntubona yuko abo bantu bakikuza kumpande zose
  26,226,Nabo bakavuga yuko aribo bavuga ivyo badashobora gushira mungiro
  26,227,"Dukuyemwo abemeye Imana yabo y’ukuri nukugira ibikorwa vyiza nuguhayagiza Imana kenshi na kenshi nukwihorana mugihe bahemukiwe ivyabo, n’ubu vuba mu bantu bahemukira abandi bazomenya ihindagurika ry’ingene bazo hindagurika"